quote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我有排都試過瞓瞓下覺得成身都痕好似有野咬咁<br />\n點知真係有蚊咬<br />\n我開住個風扇，一路吹住成個人咁瞓就冇事</blockquote><br />\n真係比蚊咬就簡單啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係幾粒一齊黎<br />\n而且蚊咬既話d粒粒冇咁快散</blockquote><br />\n我都試過<br />\n訓教唔知比咩咬但係幾粒係同一個位<br />\n仲要咬係大脾同個閪中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係癢q死 著底褲係咁磨到佢<br />\n出街癢又冇得r<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比野咬<br />\n但比野咬有咁快好返咩</blockquote><br />\n癢左我幾日幾夜<br />\n搽止癢藥膏都冇用 <br />\n係屋企直接伸手入去r<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到老公以為我下面生野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019bd3d709d84e07699a81699f399a75d949e2b2","tid":290472,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T10:21:27.000Z","msg":"有無醫生入黎講解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb7b21f4f54037e9d973d14e3231f11c77318b2","tid":290472,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"我自從出過一次風爛之後就好易敏感,以前對海鮮無事但呢排就成日出粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要一出就唔止對手有 連頸同身都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有時出街如果無帶敏感藥同藥膏真係想斬左對手落黎 夜晚成日出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無醫生可以講下咩事 係呢排先係咁"},{"pid":"398e8251f145fb59a3d1c163ce42d9f1a87063a8","tid":290472,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T00:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce73c82b5d16443cf94eddc6c87516f6bc74f97","tid":290472,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T14:18:54.000Z","msg":"又痕了"},{"pid":"a46a9668ab880e66f37691031c19346f5d415d1